---
// Comparative Section
// "O que muda quando você opera com Creative Ops" (Antes vs Depois)
---

<section class="py-[6rem] bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-[70rem] mx-auto px-[1.5rem]">
    
    <div class="text-center mb-[4rem]">
      <h2 class="text-[2rem] sm:text-[3rem] font-bold text-[#0A0A0A] mb-[1rem] leading-tight max-w-[50rem] mx-auto">
        O que muda quando você opera <br class="hidden md:block" /> com Creative Ops
      </h2>
      <p class="text-[1.125rem] text-[#737373]">
        Transforme caos em processo estruturado.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-[2rem] items-stretch">
      
      <!-- Antes (Caos) -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-[1.5rem] p-[2.5rem] shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-opacity opacity-60 hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-[1rem] mb-[2rem]">
          <div class="w-[3rem] h-[3rem] bg-[#F5F5F5] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-[#0A0A0A]">
            <svg class="w-[1.5rem] h-[1.5rem]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-[1.5rem] font-bold text-[#0A0A0A]">Modo Tradicional</h3>
        </div>
        
        <ul class="space-y-[1.25rem]">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-[1rem] text-[#737373]">
            <svg class="w-[1.25rem] h-[1.25rem] mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12"/></svg>
            <span>Briefings soltos no WhatsApp e e-mail.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-[1rem] text-[#737373]">
            <svg class="w-[1.25rem] h-[1.25rem] mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12"/></svg>
            <span>Arquivos "Final_V4" perdidos no Drive/WeTransfer.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-[1rem] text-[#737373]">
            <svg class="w-[1.25rem] h-[1.25rem] mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12"/></svg>
            <span>Cliente cobrando status a cada hora.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-[1rem] text-[#737373]">
            <svg class="w-[1.25rem] h-[1.25rem] mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12"/></svg>
            <span>Refações infinitas por falha de comunicação.</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Depois (Wikimee) -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-[1.5rem] p-[2.5rem] shadow-2xl relative overflow-hidden transform scale-105">
        
        <div class="flex items-center gap-[1rem] mb-[2rem] relative z-10">
          <div class="w-[3rem] h-[3rem] bg-[#0A0A0A] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white">
            <svg class="w-[1.5rem] h-[1.5rem]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-[1.5rem] font-bold text-[#0A0A0A]">Modo Wikimee</h3>
        </div>
        
        <ul class="space-y-[1.25rem] relative z-10">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-[1rem] text-[#0A0A0A]">
            <svg class="w-[1.25rem] h-[1.25rem] mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
            <span class="font-medium">Briefings padronizados via formulário.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-[1rem] text-[#0A0A0A]">
            <svg class="w-[1.25rem] h-[1.25rem] mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
            <span class="font-medium">Arquivos centralizados e versionados automaticamente.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-[1rem] text-[#0A0A0A]">
            <svg class="w-[1.25rem] h-[1.25rem] mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
            <span class="font-medium">Cliente acompanha o status em tempo real (self-service).</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-[1rem] text-[#0A0A0A]">
            <svg class="w-[1.25rem] h-[1.25rem] mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
            <span class="font-medium">Aprovações formais e documentadas.</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
        
        <div class="mt-[2.5rem]">
          <button 
            onclick="openModal()"
            class="px-[1.5rem] py-[0.75rem] bg-[#0A0A0A] hover:bg-[#262626] text-white font-semibold rounded-full transition-all duration-200 text-[0.9375rem] w-full sm:w-auto"
          >
            Agendar Demo
          </button>
        </div>

      </div>

    </div>

  </div>
</section>
